{
  "version": "48题通用版",
  "description": "标准评估，获得有深度的性格解读",
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "text": "同事在走廊上随口问你周末安排时，你的第一反应是心里暗想：能不能别聊了赶紧走",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "door.left.hand.closed",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "坐飞机旁边坐了个话痨陌生人，你反而觉得旅程变有趣了，聊了一路",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "airplane",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "视频会议结束后，你不急着切换窗口，而是享受终于没人说话的安静",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "work",
      "illustration": "video.slash.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "健身房遇到一个同样在练深蹲的陌生人，你会自然地搭话交流动作要领",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "leisure",
      "illustration": "figure.run",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "领导临时让你上台做即兴发言，你第一个念头是能不能让别人替你",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "stress",
      "illustration": "person.wave.2",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "搬到一个新小区的第一周，你就已经和物业、邻居、便利店老板都混熟了",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "social",
      "illustration": "house.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "text": "朋友聚餐时你在角落和一个刚认识的人聊了两个小时，其他人都在开大桌趴",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "social",
      "illustration": "bubble.left.and.bubble.right.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "text": "外卖小哥送错地址的时候，你顺便和他聊了五分钟本地的天气和路况",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "communication",
      "illustration": "delivery.truck",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "text": "团建活动被分到和不太熟的同事住一间房，你心里已经开始盘算独处时间怎么争取",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "left",
      "category": "stress",
      "illustration": "bed.double.fill",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "text": "手机没电了被困在候车室两小时，你反而认识了三个新朋友还建了群",
      "dimension": "EI",
      "direction": "right",
      "category": "communication",
      "illustration": "battery.25percent",
      "illustrationType": "sfSymbol"
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "text": "被人连续追问私人问题，你的内心OS是：能不能让我一个人待着缓缓",
